Maxima barely transformed back to tiger mode. Wounded, but in this mode, she 
was stronger. 

As Hydras put out the cease fire, she limped her way towards Hydras. Half way 
there, she glared & growled at Perceptor. 

Eventually, she made her way up to take position behind & off to the side of 
Hydras, on his right side. Her crimson optics glaring at Tyrael, a soft deep 
feline growl coming from her as she beared her razor teeth at the Tripred.
